# gw-apps.filter — Google Workspace connected apps known to be OK.
#
# One entry per line, matched against ConnectedApp.DisplayText exactly
# (case-insensitive, trimmed). A trailing '*' is a prefix rule (e.g. Google*
# matches every display name starting with "google").
#
# Listed apps are purged from UserRecord.ConnectedApps early; ThirdPartyTokens
# in the canonical snapshot reflects survivors only.
#
# Empty file ⇒ nothing filtered.

